,\"Codec ID\":\"avc1\",\"codec\":\"h264\",\"colorPrimaries\":\"bt709\",\"colorSpace\":\"bt709\",\"colorTransfer\":\"bt709\",\"duration\":178.866667,\"height\":1080,\"pixelFormat\":\"yuv420p\",\"rFrameRate\":\"30/1\",\"width\":1920}}","built_by":"render-pipeline","time_to_ready":14.465665782},"url":"https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/8bd59e9bc40fc30f4af4f4119ad36314cb7e8770.bin","created_at":1764952094,"segment_duration":3,"opt_vbitrate":5625},{"is_enhanced":false,"type":"storyboard","slug":"storyboard_2000x2240","display_name":"Storyboard","details":{},"width":2000,"height":2240,"ext":"jpg","size":570816,"bitrate":0,"public":true,"status":2,"progress":1.0,"metadata":{"frame_count":200,"aspect_ratio":1.7857143,"frame_height":112,"frame_width":200,"time_to_ready":16.69584197},"url":"https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/d0367592856d582157b4604779ed7f3c4a58b93a.bin","created_at":1764952094},{"is_enhanced":false,"type":"still_image","slug":"still_image_1920x1080","display_name":"Thumbnail Image","details":{},"width":1920,"height":1080,"size":763502,"bitrate":0,"public":true,"status":2,"progress":1.0,"metadata":{"av_stream_metadata":"{\"FastStart\":false,\"Audio\":{},\"Video\":{\"codec\":\"png\",\"colorPrimaries\":\"bt709\",\"colorSpace\":\"gbr\",\"colorTransfer\":\"iec61966-2-1\",\"height\":1080,\"pixelFormat\":\"rgba\",\"rFrameRate\":\"25/1\",\"width\":1920}}"},"url":"https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/5f4632bf757e25db56a6934f989d6201.bin","created_at":1764952094}],"branding":false,"createdAt":1760697676,"distilleryUrl":"https://distillery.wistia.com/x","duration":178.867,"enableCustomerLogo":true,"firstEmbedForAccount":false,"firstShareForAccount":false,"availableTranscripts":[{"bcp47LanguageTag":"en","familyName":"English","familyNativeName":"English","hasCaptions":true,"hasVideoStream":false,"name":"English","nativeName":"English","wistiaLanguageCode":"eng","language":"eng","ietf_language_tag":"eng","alpha3_terminologic":"eng","alpha3_bibliographic":"eng","iso639_2_language_code":"en","english_name":"English","native_name":"English","right_to_left":false,"alpha3Bibliographic":"eng","alpha3Terminologic":"eng","ietfLanguageTag":"eng","iso6392LanguageCode":"en","genericName":"English","genericNativeName":"English"}],"hashedId":"ivoqjw0mqs","mediaId":139739842,"mediaKey":"wistia-production_139739842","mediaType":"Video","name":"Sidekicks","preloadPreference":null,"progress":1.0,"protected":false,"projectId":4769430,"seoDescription":"a Scaled Customer Experience video","showAbout":true,"status":2,"type":"Video","originalIsEligibleForDirectPlayback":true,"originalFileStillAsset":{"url":"https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/23bb2c00082331332f25304105807749.jpg?video_still_time=89","width":1920,"height":1080,"type":"still_image","status":2,"public":true,"progress":1.0,"display_name":"Thumbnail image","details":{},"metadata":{}},"playableWithoutInstantHls":true,"stats":{"loadCount":6602945,"playCount":50155,"uniqueLoadCount":1974703,"uniquePlayCount":46271,"averageEngagement":0.318932},"trackingTransmitInterval":20,"liveStreamEventDetails":null,"integrations":{"google_analytics":true},"captions":[{"language":"eng","text":"Sidekicks are specialized AI agents designed to work alongside your team in Miro. Maybe you're trying to find key insights from a wall of research notes, or you need to turn the ideas from your team's brainstorm into a clear product brief, or maybe you're stuck on a design decision and need a fresh perspective. Whatever your task, there's probably a sidekick to help. And if there isn't, you can create it. We can access sidekicks by clicking the Miro AI icon. Here, we have the general sidekick to help with, well, general tasks like summarizing or synthesizing something.\n\nWe'll describe our task, select the relevant board context, and if available, connect our company's knowledge base for the sidekick to reference.\n\nWith that, it gets to work.\n\nNotice how it's gathering context by reading what's on the board and adding the output right next to it.\n\nThis general sidekick acts as an all purpose assistant, but Miro also has a library of specialized sidekicks designed for different tasks we do every day. For instance, this content design sidekick makes sure your copy and messaging is designed for most impact.\n\nThis helps write technical specifications and acceptance criteria. Or this product brief writer turns product ideas and research insights into clear and structured briefs.\n\nLet's take a closer look at this one. It's built with task specific instructions and knowledge of relevant frameworks.\n\nIt's a great starting point out of the box, but like all companies, we have our own artifacts, guidelines, and ways of doing things. So we'll customize the Sidekick to match how our team actually works.\n\nFirst, let's clone it.\n\nNow we'll review the instructions and adjust them as needed, Describe step by step how the team carries out the task.\n\nClick this button to ask AI to review and improve our instructions.\n\nFinally, in the knowledge source, we'll upload critical documents like strategy artifacts, methodologies, and examples as reference.\n\nThis ensures that every output the Sidekick generates is informed by our company's context.\n\nThen save and our new Sidekick is ready to be used.\n\nShare Sidekicks with colleagues or publish them to the Miroverse.\n\nAnd that's it. In Sidekicks, you have expert teammates helping you move faster every step of the way.\n\nExplore them and see what your team can build."}],"hls_enabled":true,"embed_options":{"opaqueControls":"false","playerColor":"050038","playerColorGradient":{"on":false,"colors":[["#2949E5",0],["#8fafff",1]],"on":"false","colors":[["#2949E5","0"],["#8fafff","1"]]},"plugin":{"captions":{"on":"true"},"midrollLink-v1":{"links":[{"active":"true","conversionOpportunityKey":"wistia-production_8284389","duration":"194","name":"annotation_1762437149253_2765","text":"Beta","time":"0","url":"","theme":"dark